description:
Agnes Varda gives life to an Opera telling and showing the love, the life of people that are on Street Mouffetard, "La Mouffe". This ideias are taken from a notebook of a pregnant woman. Old people, Lovers, children, workers make a composition together with the music that is sang, that was in charge of Georges Delarue. A visual poetry
